title: Kubernetes: Node and Cluster Level Filesystem Usage
agents: kubernetes
catalog: containerization/kubernetes
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check and the associated special agent (agent_kubernetes) are deprecated
 and will be removed in Checkmk version 2.2.0.

 Please configure the new special agent using the "Kubernetes" ruleset.

 This check monitors at cluster and node level the filesystem's usage.
item:
 The logical disk partition filesystem.

discovery:
 One service is created for each filesystem.
